ce that you require no matter how small or large of a job it may be.[/inwave_heading][inwave_button style=\"button2\" button_text=\"About us\" button_size=\"button-small\" background_color=\"bg-grey\" shape=\"rounded\" align=\"right\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][inwave_testimonial_item style=\"style2\" name=\"Daniel Nguyen \" position=\"Vietnamese client \" image=\"274\" rate=\"0\"]I wanted to THANK the Team for servicing and repairing my Harley Davidson on such short notice. The window works just like new.It is good to know that there are Service companies out there that still stand behind their work and their service[/inwave_testimonial_item][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row iw_layout=\"wide-bg\" css=\".vc_custom_1460016490316{padding-top: 40px !important;background-color: #0f0f0f !important;}\"][vc_column][inwave_heading title=\"Six reasons why choose us\" font_weight_title=\"700\" align=\"center\" preview_style1=\"\" css=\".vc_custom_1467965847279{padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][/inwave_heading][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1460016395876{padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][inwave_info_item style=\"style4\" title=\"PREMIUM QUALITY\" icon_size=\"86\" icon_img=\"498\"]We guarantee quality of our works from the  diagnostic to repairs.[/inwave_info_item][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][inwave_info_item style=\"style4\" title=\"Dependable Services\" icon_size=\"86\" icon_img=\"503\"]We love to take pride in the work we do. Each project is finished in time and budget[/inwave_info_item][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][inwave_info_item style=\"style4\" title=\"Reputable Company\" icon_size=\"86\" icon_img=\"502\"]Operating for more than 30 years, earning a reputation for service and beautiful work[/inwave_info_item][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1460016412252{padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][inwave_info_item style=\"style4\" title=\"Free Consultations\" icon_size=\"86\" icon_img=\"501\"]We offer free consultations for our services, and will provide you with an actual quote[/inwave_info_item][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][inwave_info_item style=\"style4\" title=\"ONLINE SERVICE\" icon_size=\"86\" icon_img=\"500\"]You can be assured of our support 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.[/inwave_info_item][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][inwave_info_item style=\"style4\" title=\"EXCLUSIVE OFFERS\" icon_size=\"86\" icon_img=\"499\"]Motorcycles repair is carried out at a highly professional level.[/inwave_info_item][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row iw_layout=\"wide-bg\" iw_parallax=\"1\" iw_parallax_overlay=\"0\" css=\".vc_custom_1460079790251{padding-top: 85px !important;padding-bottom: 85px !important;background-image: url(http://localhost:85/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/page-form-background.jpg?id=513) !important;}\" el_class=\"contact7-form\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][inwave_heading title=\"OUR MAIN PRINCIPLES\" sub_title=\"Bike Hero ADVANTAGES\" font_weight_title=\"700\" preview_style1=\"\" css=\".vc_custom_1460365508751{padding-top: 0px !important;}\"][/inwave_heading][vc_column_text]We offer lower prices for services and spare parts than branded stations. We use information databases of European, Japanese and Korean motorcycle manufacturers for motorcycle repairs. We offer new motorcycle servicing. In its basis is an individual approach and cost optimization for our clients.\n<h3>MOTORCYCLE AWARDS</h3>\nWith so many years of experience in the business, our company is your source for the highest quality and motorcycle repair &amp; chopper service.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class=\"branding-logos\"]<a href=\"#\"><img src=\"http://localhost:85/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/page-logo-brand-1.png\" alt=\"page-logo-brand-1\" /></a><a href=\"#\"><img src=\"http://localhost:85/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/pag